wgInfoModule.name: wgInfoModule
wgInfoModule.contactinfo: Ella Yu WatchGuard Technologies, Inc. 1841 Zanker Road San Jose, CA 95112 USA 408-519-4888 ella.yu@watchguard.com
wgInfoModule.description: The MIB module describes various tunnel objects of WatchGuard system.

wgIpsecTunnelMIB.name: wgIpsecTunnelMIB
wgIpsecTunnelMIB.description: This is the base object identifier for all tunnel branches.

wgIpsecTunnel.name: wgIpsecTunnel
wgIpsecTunnel.description: This is the base object identifier for all tunnel information.

wgIpsecTunnelNum.name: wgIpsecTunnelNum
wgIpsecTunnelNum.description: The total number of entries in the wgIpsecTunnelTable.

wgIpsecTunnelTable.name: wgIpsecTunnelTable
wgIpsecTunnelTable.description: This is the connection table describing all current tunnels exist on this entity.

wgIpsecTunnelEntry.name: wgIpsecTunnelEntry
wgIpsecTunnelEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) containing the information on a tunnel between two security gateways.

wgIpsecTunnelID.name: wgIpsecTunnelID
wgIpsecTunnelID.description: The running index of this tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelLocalAddr.name: wgIpsecTunnelLocalAddr
wgIpsecTunnelLocalAddr.description: The local IP address of the current tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelPeerAddr.name: wgIpsecTunnelPeerAddr
wgIpsecTunnelPeerAddr.description: The remote IP address of the current tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelInSpi.name: wgIpsecTunnelInSpi
wgIpsecTunnelInSpi.description: The security parameters index of inbound SA's within this tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelOutSpi.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutSpi
wgIpsecTunnelOutSpi.description: The security parameters index of outbound SA's within this tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelCreateTime.name: wgIpsecTunnelCreateTime
wgIpsecTunnelCreateTime.description: The date and time when the tunnel is created.

wgIpsecTunnelDeviceID.name: wgIpsecTunnelDeviceID
wgIpsecTunnelDeviceID.description: The identifier of target device where the SA resides.

wgIpsecTunnelEspEncryptAlg.name: wgIpsecTunnelEspEncryptAlg
wgIpsecTunnelEspEncryptAlg.description: The encryption algorithm used in the tunnel. It's 0 if ESP is not used.

wgIpsecTunnelEspAuthAlg.name: wgIpsecTunnelEspAuthAlg
wgIpsecTunnelEspAuthAlg.description: The authentication algorithm used in the tunnel. It's 0 if ESP is not used.

wgIpsecTunnelAhAuthAlg.name: wgIpsecTunnelAhAuthAlg
wgIpsecTunnelAhAuthAlg.description: The AH authentication algorithm used in the tunnel. It's 0 if AH is not used.

wgIpsecTunnelMode.name: wgIpsecTunnelMode
wgIpsecTunnelMode.description: The tunnel/transport mode of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelKeyMode.name: wgIpsecTunnelKeyMode
wgIpsecTunnelKeyMode.description: The key mode of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelLifeTime.name: wgIpsecTunnelLifeTime
wgIpsecTunnelLifeTime.description: The life time (in hundredths of a second) of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelLifeLength.name: wgIpsecTunnelLifeLength
wgIpsecTunnelLifeLength.description: The maximum traffic in bytes that the tunnel is allowed to support.

wgIpsecTunnelInSaBytes.name: wgIpsecTunnelInSaBytes
wgIpsecTunnelInSaBytes.description: Current active inbound SA bytes of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelOutSaBytes.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutSaBytes
wgIpsecTunnelOutSaBytes.description: Current active outbound SA bytes of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelAccSecs.name: wgIpsecTunnelAccSecs
wgIpsecTunnelAccSecs.description: The number of seconds that the tunnel has existed.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorProtocol.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorProtocol
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorProtocol.description: The ip protocol number that this SA selector carries, or 0 if it carries any protocol.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPType.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPType
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPType.description: The type of remote IP address of the SA selector in the entity.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPOne.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPOne
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPOne.description: The first remote IP address of the SA selector in the entity. It's IP address if remote IP of this selector only has one address. It's IP address of subnet if the remote IP of this selector is IP subnet. It's the start IP address if the remote IP of this selector has a range of addresses.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPTwo.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPTwo
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemoteIPTwo.description: The second remote IP address of the SA selector in the entity. It's 0 if remote IP of this selector only has one address. It's netmask of subnet if the remote IP of this selector is IP subnet. It's the end IP address if the remote IP of this selector has a range of addresses.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemotePort.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemotePort
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorRemotePort.description: The remote port used by this selector in the entity.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPType.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPType
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPType.description: The type of local IP address of the SA selector in the entity.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPOne.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPOne
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPOne.description: The first local IP address of the SA selector in the entity. It's IP address if local IP of this selector only has one address. It's IP address of subnet if the local IP of this selector is IP subnet. It's the start IP address if the local IP of this selector has a range of IP addresses.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPTwo.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPTwo
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalIPTwo.description: The second local IP address of the SA selector in the entity. It's 0 if local IP of this selector only has one address. It's netmask of subnet if the local IP of this selector is IP subnet. It's the end IP address if the local IP of this selector has a range of IP addresses.

wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalPort.name: wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalPort
wgIpsecTunnelSelectorLocalPort.description: The local port used by this selector in the entity.

wgIpsecTunnelNumRekey.name: wgIpsecTunnelNumRekey
wgIpsecTunnelNumRekey.description: The number of rekeys of the tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelInKbytes.name: wgIpsecTunnelInKbytes
wgIpsecTunnelInKbytes.description: Total inbound traffic in Kbytes since the establish of this tunnel.

wgIpsecTunnelOutKbytes.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutKbytes
wgIpsecTunnelOutKbytes.description: Total outound traffic in Kbytes since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelInPackets.name: wgIpsecTunnelInPackets
wgIpsecTunnelInPackets.description: Total number of inbound packets since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelOutPackets.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutPackets
wgIpsecTunnelOutPackets.description: Total number of outound packets since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelInDecryptErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelInDecryptErrors
wgIpsecTunnelInDecryptErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to decryption error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelInAuthErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelInAuthErrors
wgIpsecTunnelInAuthErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to authentication error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelInReplayErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelInReplayErrors
wgIpsecTunnelInReplayErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to replay error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelInOtherErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelInOtherErrors
wgIpsecTunnelInOtherErrors.description: The number of packets discarded due to errors other than decryption, authentication or replay errors. This may include packets dropped due to a lack of receive buffers, and may include packets dropped due to congestion at the decryption element.

wgIpsecTunnelOutDecryptErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutDecryptErrors
wgIpsecTunnelOutDecryptErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to decryption error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelOutAuthErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutAuthErrors
wgIpsecTunnelOutAuthErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to authentication error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelOutReplayErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutReplayErrors
wgIpsecTunnelOutReplayErrors.description: Total number of packets discarded due to replay error since the establish of this connection.

wgIpsecTunnelOutOtherErrors.name: wgIpsecTunnelOutOtherErrors
wgIpsecTunnelOutOtherErrors.description: The number of packets discarded due to errors other than decryption, authentication or replay errors. This may include packets dropped due to a lack of receive buffers, and may include packets dropped due to congestion at the decryption element.

wgIpsecTunnelUdpEncap.name: wgIpsecTunnelUdpEncap
wgIpsecTunnelUdpEncap.description: Indicates whether if UDP encapsulated IPSec has been enabled.

wgIpsecTunnelPeerUdpPort.name: wgIpsecTunnelPeerUdpPort
wgIpsecTunnelPeerUdpPort.description: The peer's UDP port of current tunnel when UDP encapsulated IPSec is enabled.

wgIpsecTunnelOrigPeerAddr.name: wgIpsecTunnelOrigPeerAddr
wgIpsecTunnelOrigPeerAddr.description: The original peer ip address of current tunnel when UDP encapsulated IPSec is enabled
